- if (planid) 
  p
    | Ok, we're almost ready to go! Share this link with anybody
    | with whom you'd like to plan your week. Click the link 
    | to get started.
  p(style= 'text-align: center') 
    a(href = '/' + planid ) 
      | http://dinnerplanner.herokuapp.com/#{ planid }
- else
  .start_planning
    p
      | DISCLAIMER: "What's For Dinner" is still a very young project, 
      | and it's not finished yet. Don't be surprised when things don't work.
      | Please do not run any critical health support systems on this software.
    p
      | To get started, click to generate a new
      | planner for your week. You will get a link
      | to share.
    form(method= 'post', action='/')
      input(type= 'submit', value= 'Start Planning!')  

